        dc:description           "Figure 15. Cytochrome c oxidase subunit 1 amino acid sequences from Peixoto et al. (2018). Boxes indicate diagnostic molecular characters. For each sequence a unique corresponding DNA voucher code is listed as BJS followed by a number." , "Figure 14. Eadya spitzer Ridenbaugh, sp. n. paratype. A Head, frontal view B Head, dorsal view C Head and mesoscutum, dorsal view D Mesopleuron, lateral view E Propodeum, dorsal view." , "Figure 13. Eadya spitzer Ridenbaugh, sp. n. paratype. A Lateral habitus B Dorsal habitus C Metasoma, lateral view. All scale bars are 1 mm in length." , "Figure 12. Eadya spitzer Ridenbaugh, sp. n. holotype. A Lateral habitus B Dorsal habitus C Metasoma, lateral view. All scale bars are 1 mm in length." ;
